casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Linder.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Linder (1994), 70 Ohio St.3d 1201.]

(No. 94-1314 Submitted July 27, 1994 Decided July 29, 1994.)

The resignation of Robert Alan Linder of Batavia, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0031794, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
